{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DESIGNED AS 2-PLAYER CO-OP</strong></h2>Co-op mode for 2 players is not a supplementary or optional way of playing Njorun's Will - it is rather the only intended way to do it. All the game mechanics and experiences are designed and built with &quot;co-opness&quot; in mind.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/extras/shrine-gif-1000px.gif?t=1681302368\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>TELEKINETIC ABILITIES</strong></h2>Playing as K\u00e6ra Scouts, you can telekinetically manipulate each other as well as various objects in the game. Use this power to overcome the obstacles and help each other.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/extras/bridge-gif-1050px.gif?t=1681302368\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CHALLENGING COMBAT</strong></h2>Study the enemies and coordinate your actions to be victorious in fights. Mistakes are costly, resources are limited.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/extras/creature-fight-cut-crop-steam-edit.gif?t=1681302368\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>EXPLORATION AND INVESTIGATION</strong></h2>Your primary goal is to solve the mystery. Observe the surroundings, explore the houses and dungeons, talk to strangers. Find the answers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/extras/fire-barrel-house.gif?t=1681302368\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PLATFORMING AND PUZZLES</strong></h2>You will need to perform high-precision movements and jumps to traverse the locations. At times, moving forward won't be possible without scratching your head and solving a puzzle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/extras/shield-jumping-crop.gif?t=1681302368\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WANT TO KNOW MORE? JOIN OUR DISCORD COMMUNITY!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/extras/wishlist_and_follow.png?t=1681302368\" /></h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1681302368","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/page.bg.jpg?t=1681302368","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1681302368","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1681302368","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2222290,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>PLAY ON STEAM USING THE REMOTE PLAY TOGETHER FEATURE</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678040/extras/RPT.png?t=1681302368\" /></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DESIGNED AS 2-PLAYER CO-OP</strong></h2>Co-op mode for 2 players is not a supplementary or optional way of playing Njorun's Will - it is rather the only intended way to do it. All the game mechanics and experiences are designed and built with &quot;co-opness&quot; in mind.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/16780